      },
      {
        "segment": "Is this the way these concepts came about on this planet?",
        "start_offset": 180,
        "end_offset": 237,
        "start": 22.501,
        "end": 26.601
      },
      {
        "segment": "Because if we go back to the beginning of third density, there must be a primal cause of this.",
