        "start": 58.263,
        "end": 59.383
      },
      {
        "segment": "We shall attempt.",
        "start_offset": 452,
        "end_offset": 469,
        "start": 59.403,
        "end": 59.763
      },
      {
        "segment": "The sexual energy transfers and blockages are more a manifestation or example of that which is more fundamental than the other way about.",
        "start_offset": 470,
        "end_offset": 607,
        "start": 59.783,
        "end": 80.164
      },
      {
        "segment": "Therefore, as your peoples became open to the concepts of bellicosity and the greed of ownership, these various distortions then began to filter down through the tree of mind into body complex expressions, the sexual expression being basic to that complex.",
        "start_offset": 608,
        "end_offset": 864,
        "start": 81.584,
        "end": 135.126
      },
      {
        "segment": "Thus these sexual energy blockages, though Orion influenced and intensified, are basically the product of the beingness chosen freely by your peoples.",
